HEADWORD: outlandishness
<hw>out*land"ish*ness</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being
strikingly out of the ordinary; the quality of being
outlandish{2}.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bizarreness, weirdness.</syn>⟦br⟧
